cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM 

This paper deals with image change detection using an on-board monocular vision system, which is a fundamental problem in intelligent vehicle (IV). Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV). The paper proposes a new autoencoder-based framework that combines anomaly detection and image compression, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed method is also applicable to robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM) applications.
